    11→ *
    12→ * ## Lifecycle
    13→ * - Lazy-initialised on first call to `getV2Coordinator()`.
    14→ * - Call `destroyV2Coordinator()` during process shutdown to release
    15→ *   all active sessions cleanly.
    16→ *
    17→ * ## Rules
    18→ * - No OpenAI imports.
